BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:📡 Anil Menon Pre-Flight News Conference
DTSTART:20260429T174500Z
DTEND:20260429T194500Z
DTSTAMP:20260425T071256Z
UID:2d832165-event@nasa-events-ics
DESCRIPTION:Type: Press Event\n\nNASA will host a news conference from the
  agency’s Johnson Space Center in Houston to preview astronaut Anil Meno
 n’s upcoming mission to the International Space Station.\n\nThe Soyuz MS
 -29 mission\, targeted to launch Tuesday\, July 14\, will carry Menon and 
 his crewmates\, Roscosmos cosmonauts Pyotr Dubrov and Anna Kikina\, to the
  International Space Station for an eight-month stay as part of Expedition
 s 74/75. It will be Menon’s first spaceflight.\n\nDetails: https://ll.th
 espacedevs.com/2.3.0/events/1448/?format=json
URL:https://ll.thespacedevs.com/2.3.0/events/1448/?format=json
END:VEVENT
